      • getAttributeName

        public String getAttributeName()
        Description copied from interface: DeleteRequest
        The attribute name tells the CatalogProvider implementer what type of attribute values are in the (DeleteRequest.getAttributeValues()) List. For instance, if the attribute name was "id," then the CatalogProvider implementer would know that the attribute values in the list were id values (such as 575aa9625fa24b338bd3c439f2613709 ).
        Specified by:
